OL,3,CJersey's 'backdoor into the UK'
OL,4,Ccondemned by MPs
OL,6,FHowever, UK MPs are now flagging it as
OL,7,Fa risk to their own border security.
OL,9,FChris Philp, the UK's Shadow Home
OL,10,FSecretary and Conservative MP for
OL,11,FCroydon South, says "our concern is
OL,12,Fthat French ID cards are not
OL,13,Fparticularly secure documents - it is
OL,14,Fpossible to forge them relatively
OL,15,Feasily.
OL,17,F"And because the Channel Islands are
OL,18,Fpart of the Common Travel Area, the
OL,19,Fchecks between the Channel Islands and
OL,20,Fthe UK mainland are nothing like as
OL,21,Fstrict as a regular passport control."
