OL,3,CJersey's 'backdoor into the UK'
OL,4,Ccondemned by MPs
OL,6,FWhilst no person has been identified
OL,7,Fto have exploited the scheme in this
OL,8,Fway in the past two years, Philp
OL,9,Fargues "concerns about border control
OL,10,Fare higher now than they ever have
OL,11,Fbeen."
OL,13,FCiting rising number of immigrants
OL,14,Fwho've made their way to the UK on
OL,15,Fsmall boats from Calais, he argues
OL,16,FJersey's scheme leaves a chink in the
OL,17,FUK's armour that has the power to
OL,18,F"snowball into something much larger"
OL,19,Fif left unaddressed.
