OL,3,CJersey's 'backdoor into the UK'
OL,4,Ccondemned by MPs
OL,6,F"When you have a vulnerability with
OL,7,Fyour border security, what can start
OL,8,Foff as a very small problem can
OL,9,Frapidly grow as illegal immigrants and
OL,10,Fothers exploit vulnerabilities", he
OL,11,Fsays.
OL,13,FPhilp hasn't raised concerns with
OL,14,Fmembers of Jersey's government
OL,15,Fdirectly.
