OL,6,FGuernsey is in the process of deciding
OL,7,Fwhether to extend their version of the
OL,8,Fscheme for another year.
OL,10,FA Guernsey Government spokesperson
OL,11,Fsays: "It is the intention in Guernsey
OL,12,Fto extend the French Identity Card
OL,13,FScheme locally, on the condition it
OL,14,Fdoes not place our membership of the
OL,15,FCommon Travel Area at risk.
